jde.wizards
Class MethodFactory

java.lang.Object
  jde.wizards.MethodFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClassRegistry
Direct Known Subclasses:
DelegateFactory, InterfaceFactory, MethodOverrideFactory
public class MethodFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClassRegistry

Defines a factory for creating skeleton implementations of Java interfaces. The factory can be invoked from the command line or from another program. The factory can generate implementations for multiple interfaces when invoked from the command line. Copyright (C) 1998-2004 Eric D. Friedman . All Rights Reserved. getMethodSkeletonExpression

public java.lang.String getMethodSkeletonExpression(Signature sig)
Get a Lisp form that generates a skeleton implementation of a specified method. The List form is of the form (jde-wiz-gen-method ... ) where jde-wiz-gen-method is a function defined by the JDEE's jde-wiz package.

Returns:
a String value
